file.name: form_param.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.0.1
  title: test
paths:
  /foo:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
                format:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/ImageFormat'
                uploadDate:
                  type: string
                  format: date-time
                  readOnly: true
                image:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
              required:
              - image
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Foo
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
      tags:
        - Foos
      operationId: getFoo
components:
  schemas:
    ImageFormat:
      type: string
      enum:
        - gif
        - jpeg
        - png
      x-ms-enum:
        name: ImageType
        modelAsString: true
